45Z","bug_reporter_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2018-12-12T14:38:03.537Z","team_member_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2019-01-11T13:39:12.351Z","comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"**Summary:** \nprotocol \u0026 Ports are not shown in third-party site redirect warning page \n\n**Vulnerable Endpoint :-** https://www.semrush.com/redirect?url=ftp://evil.com:1337\n\n**Description:** \nI noticed #311330 this report where you guys fixed a open redirect report by adding a external third-party site redirect warning page . It was a great fix . Although a issue caught in my eye . Urls contains a **protocol** and **Ports** . If I add a url with any other **protocol** like **ftp://** then it's not shown in the external warning page what can be used to take a user to any other place then user expected to go  .\n\n## Browsers Verified In:\n  * All Browsers .\n## Steps To Reproduce:\n* Visit https://www.semrush.com/redirect?url=ftp://evil.com:1337\n* You will see a warning page only saying about the domain but no warning about the **protocol \u0026 Port** like below :- {F387701}\n* But the source says it will take user to **ftp://evil.com:1337** not only **evil.com**\n\n```\n\u003ca href=\"ftp://evil.com:1337\" id=\"js-site-link\" class=\"site_link\" data-test-site-link=\"\"\u003e\nGo to site \u003c/a\u003e\n```\n## Supporting Material/References:\n* {F387701}\n* {F387702}\n\n## Impact\n\nI noticed in **url=** parameter many protocols can be used . Like I can use **vnc://** protocol and on my mac os if I visit **https://www.semrush.com/redirect?url=ftp://evil.com:1337** and click on **Go to site** then it will open my mac environment's default VNC app like below screenshot :-\n{F387702}\n\nSo while user may think they will visit a site but actually they will request to a site with a protocol what may take them to anything else .\n\n##FIX :-\nI can suggest 2 possible fix here :-\n* Show the  **protocol \u0026 Ports** of the inputted url in the Warning page .\n* Or only allow users to add **HTTP \u0026 HTTPS** protocol .\n\nThanks .","weakness":{"id":53,"name":"Open Redirect"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":387701,"file_name":"Screenshot_2018-12-09_at_3.56.14_PM.png","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/000/387/701/c269f683c8784b475d64d64ebbf3962f34b53b2e/Screenshot_2018-12-09_at_3.56.14_PM.png?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22Screenshot_2018-12-09_at_3.56.14_PM.png%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27Screenshot_2018-12-09_at_3.56.14_PM.png\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fpng\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQQIRQPFMU%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T093847Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECgaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIQDcXQw%2BKjgQDHd%2FGPQ6paEVuWbBuM%2FZeCIr4OwLUNW5mAIgajaxd1seALNlR4oLY%2BSWs0RDtdqA6B%2F0l%2BLG0kaMzaEqugUI8f%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FARADGgwwMTM2MTkyNzQ4NDkiDOaFqgYYJ8y8L84BeSqOBaB8woOFlxAnT%2BAbMd6Q%2BA7KnKENRky9Al39SMa0h48dYatFmMN%2FPHZRHOj%2Fcs8Xuh0Say%2BdSuypedVpGNLkyuNrBQA5NV9C6uhJdriImYFLSoTJRrp0hsmk0QaTsplu7%2Bbw%2ByMgH1FIiRm5D9ZemtWIfVelW3lzvYc7YdSWlfPjbpyK43XVmtXSXhxI%2FeH0AdWMgu76a3mfc3eObIafNKr%2Ba%2B04uIH0kpP1lWfvRmkYmgmrUDfu%2BaFMKspfVcyFPkCvMHKe26rgJg4ZJDu7R2d6mEs7jv3Y9rO9Ak9gm4QSUuCOhln25oTFHHHc9%2Bk6f1qAHgqum%2BOLFvFLJpg9NUnNr4Cri8ZwLinOSXuWLThOE8vsvo9JU7%2FQ18eS3sKEz%2B9sVK%2B04Lph%2B3dwqxV4fbO9SPlzx80oLidlVAZb70nDAWUwJqbZN49eHJQU0YrOt%2Ba3ployIjz2IkGzHNlMJTJeJ86hjeYrlccFGsjH41tWPPBDli4GDDllxYmbNNiSeOu6l9QeKsLKlIo%2Ffh8m4uVsLclVx6wDG9XfM%2FW2dVx75kI6xUtM%2BD3jxfopl4MjSj%2BD4%2BED0gBodevdiAiowk0vauoXgELtYA5Jn3oDsnLsliKLYSlQSsxqB7EKbLtZbbsXGfTv89yfg5UHgPKyf0gChkJsAgc3QapYAGbMpFDWhmuGjeMaGNptzS3rkOvOwbOv7AUrl6rumiGQPQVaWNJB0feqlDhzRlBVBRWLcvf8X8Dk8ZIgfq06IOq2p1Gf%2BMuNp1QXjtg0QL8KXJM5sJIUkEjrpUg%2F62v7zB%2BEqULtJ0rrX2u9zQaAI77Rw